  "notes": [
    [
      "Joseph: a lot of the ones {differences} from season 2 are that we removed grass from a bunch of the images because there was this original idea that the underground Solver's headquarters somehow had a greenery growing in it (which we did keep to some degree - there is a garden in s2), but we felt like it no longer felt like you were in an underground academy-like place with too much grass around \nand the story just didn't explore the whole underground greenery thing enough to really warrant having it everywhere",
