    [
      "Joshep: a note on the one with photo of the 8 founders: you can see we removed a character to keep a sense of mystery - don't expect that the character shown there is necessarily who the 8th founder actually is (like genuinely, the decision of which character to remove was just \"well this one is at the edge and is easy to remove\") \nwe may keep that character design, we may not\ncanonically, the 8th founder has not been shown",
