    ],
    [
      "When asked 'Any interesting reason why 2x50 and 2x51 were swapped?' Joshep replied: I think it was because the puzzles matched the art a bit better",
      [
        "2",
        "50"
      ],
      [
        "2",
        "51"
      ]
    ],
    [
      "Joshep: I think there was a different version of the story where the garden/branch theming made more sense, but yeah, it {the floating branch} didn't survive, haha",
      [
        "2",
        "38"
      ],
      [
        "2",
        "39"
      ]
    ],
    [
      "Joshep: basically, there were some really quite confusing arcs in the original version of the story, and Pip did some surgical wizardry to simplify things while keeping the story intact and without us having to change any puzzles\nthe one remnant of that is that slightly weird bit where the rival says \"oh, our assignments were mixed up, your assignment is over there\"\nbut in the grand scheme of things, that one moment is less confusing than the way it was originally",
